---

title: Contact

---

:javascript
  window.onload = (function(){
    if(window.location.hash == '#thank-you'){
      document.getElementById('thank-you-message').className = 'alert alert-success';
    }
  })


.container
  .row
    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.mt-60
      #thank-you-message.hidden{:role => "alert"}
        Merci de m'avoir contacté, je vous répondrai dès que possible. :)
  %form.row{:action => "https://formspree.io/r.rigault@me.com", :method => "post"}

    %input{:name => "_next", :type => "hidden", :value => "https://www.remyrigault.pro/contact/#thank-you"}/

    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-2
      .form-group
        %input.form-control{:name => "name", :placeholder => "Prénom", :type => "text", :required => "", "data-validation" => "required"}/

    .col-md-4
      .form-group
        %input.form-control{:name => "last name", :placeholder => "Nom", :type => "text", :required => "", "data-validation" => "required"}/

    .clearfix

    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
      .form-group
        %input.form-control{:name => "_replyto", :placeholder => "Email", :type => "email", :required => "", "data-validation" => "email"}/

    .clearfix

    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
      .form-group
        %textarea.form-control{:name => "message", :placeholder => "Message", :rows => "3"}


      %input.btn.btn-link.link.text-uppercase.btn-lg{:type => "submit", :value => "Envoyer"}
